From: Joerg Roedel <jroedel@suse.de>
Date: Wed, 29 Apr 2020 15:37:00 +0200
Subject: iommu/mediatek: Convert to probe/release_device() call-backs
Git-commit: 80e4592a77e4baa33035eaeac646f63f1f5d3d57
Patch-mainline: v5.8-rc1
References: bsc#1175713

Convert the Mediatek IOMMU driver to use the probe_device() and
release_device() call-backs of iommu_ops, so that the iommu core code
does the group and sysfs setup.

Signed-off-by: Joerg Roedel <jroedel@suse.de>
Link: https://lore.kernel.org/r/20200429133712.31431-23-joro@8bytes.org
Signed-off-by: Joerg Roedel <jroedel@suse.de>
